column4: NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "6B61CAF8461DFEC0D3DF09A6D75B3558", "I don\'t think they can remember my orders.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "876973B6482DF41CF33D7EABAD077B20", "They don\'t understand now. They should be bringing me my meals, but....")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "45287B5741CA99075D293B9FD0594713", "While I was working, they didn\'t bring my meals, so I forgot to eat.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "2D628317497927332F066DB6829B804E", "You\'re too wrapped up in your work.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "98201F09449A40682E62E694B33E29F1", "I think there\'s trouble in the mansion.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "5585DD1E4B29FB8333A178BE6CB3E781", "Any problem on the island? Is everyone like my men?")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "9C623B6F4FF961D2140A38BEC44AEFA6", "Do you think someone is planning this?")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "5CE90101403AFAF33805D8AAA28ED96D", "We\'re building a city to unite the hearts of Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "2D4915F84A985AB4A103D48280658EC5", "What can I do? My men only have fighting skills.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "E361E25446F5DDC7DB7A08AF7C7C8A80", "Let me think about it. I\'m very sorry.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "5DF3A2AC4CCA95CC9B602FB8CAF727B7", "I\'ll come back again. Don\'t forget to eat.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "9C9794B44FC88B625597309FBEB266D0", "A match? That\'s perfect. It will refresh my men.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EA569A3A420A518A2EF7F29B9F2BDDB8]", "B75289ED4A9754446E3B6E95E04B592F", "Yes, but I still have some research to do. I\'ll go there soon.")
